Use this page to open Pull requests for changes to the Bitcoin Core project
website at [aixcoincore.org](https://aixcoincore.org).

[aixcoin.org](https://aixcoin.org) is not connected with or maintained by the
Bitcoin Core project contributors. Pull requests for changes to that website
should be opened at [the aixcoin.org
repository](https://github.com/aixcoin-dot-org/aixcoin.org/pulls).

General aixcoin questions and/or support requests are best directed to the
Bitcoin StackExchange at https://aixcoin.stackexchange.com.
